title: A Scatter Plot of Palmer Penguins
text:
import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns 
from palmerpenguins import load_penguins
import dabest
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
penguins = load_penguins()
sns.scatterplot(data = penguins, x = 'bill_length_mm', y = 'body_mass_g', hue = 'species');

title: A Contrast Plot of Palmer Penguins
text:
import pandas as pd
import dabest
from palmerpenguins import load_penguins
import dabest
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib
import warnings
warnings.filterwarnings("ignore")
penguins = load_penguins()
a = dabest.load(data = penguins, x = 'species', idx = tuple(penguins.species.unique()), y = 'body_mass_g');
f = a.mean_diff.plot();
